# Local data
#  SPICE kernels (data/kernels/*.bsp etc.) and the Natural Earth coastline
#  (web/public/data/*) are now tracked in this repo so a fresh clone runs
#  without any runtime network fetches. `pixi run kernels` is only needed
#  when bumping kernel versions; CI verifies sha256 in manifest.toml.
#  Only the transient runtime cache stays ignored:
data/cache/

